-- Chelsea Defender David Luiz Signs Five-Year Contract, Club Says
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-09-22T18:11:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-22/chelsea-defender-david-luiz-signs-five-year-contract-club-says.html
Chelsea defender  David Luiz  signed
a new five-year contract, the Premier League soccer club said on
its website.  Luiz, 25, has started 55 of 59 games he’s played since
joining Chelsea from Benfica in 2001. The Brazil international
has scored five goals.  Luiz’s new contract runs until 2017.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  